com.intel.icecp.core.pipeline

Interface Operations

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OperationsImpl

    public interface Operations
    Interface for operations creation, using a provider pattern; the interface exposes methods to register and obtain OperationProvider, and to build Operation from attributes.
